# Getting Started

## Installation

Jaringan is installed from source via Cargo:

```
cargo install --path crates/jaringan-browser
```

## Your First Page

Create a file called hello.jrg:

```
# Hello World

Welcome to Jaringan!

=> https://example.com Visit Example
```

Open it with:

```
jaringan-browser open hello.jrg
```

